name: Minimal Playstore & Appstore Template
description:
Simple, clean and minimal play store and app store template for your application.

Just simply edit your content(Text & Screens) and export.


Screens Included:

  • Mobile(Light) - 5 Screens
  • Mobile(Dark) - 5 Screens
  • Tablet(Light) - 2 Screens
  • Tablet(Dark) - 2 Screens
